        crossfadeSeconds: 0.2
    - rid: 4444056937922035889
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: 405f9ba8a7d24b629a9a7202a884f3dd
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: ????
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Oh, I love that old trick with the petals! Kaitora's really just a
          hopeless romantic at heart.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: b38f426ce77044dca3f0f71c712b7d2f
    - rid: 4444056937922035892
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: 10b704a2597c4868bcb180f4388f1e07
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: One thing about us, is we turn every strong feeling into magic. I mean,
          how cool is that? Now, let's see if we vibe.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056937922035893
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: ef7284d3bce04e879549f93207a0fc4d
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Are you someone who is more organized or playful?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056937922035896
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: c8df9113415f4f728eea3dc4fa425e26
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: I'm more organized, than playful.
          nextStepId: 8eb91c3b4a854860bc0eeb810c9f9ef2
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: ' I''m more playful, than organized. '
          nextStepId: 8eb91c3b4a854860bc0eeb810c9f9ef2
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 4444056937922035897
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: 8eb91c3b4a854860bc0eeb810c9f9ef2
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Hold on! I'm writing that down. Just kidding. My memory's impeccable.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 0eabfacdc43d4e2a81b03971b87fc5c9
    - rid: 4444056937922035902
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: 0eabfacdc43d4e2a81b03971b87fc5c9
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: And this brings us to our next question. I swear, it's part of the
          assignment...
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056937922035903
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: 22ccc12316c946628a04064073341518
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: What does your ideal weekend look like?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 26703e08e2574211ba5e52862655239e
    - rid: 4444056937922035904
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: 26703e08e2574211ba5e52862655239e
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: Hanging out with friends. It really boosts my energy!
          nextStepId: 1bf0b5b640e146b8821b74f58d838783
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: 'Staying in, doing my favorite things, so I can recharge. '
          nextStepId: 1bf0b5b640e146b8821b74f58d838783
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 4444056937922035905
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: 1bf0b5b640e146b8821b74f58d838783
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Nice one. And I got all my answers! I guess, we can call it a day...
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: cbfa21a984714d718e2d0eaab9b51bf9
    - rid: 4444056937922035906
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: cbfa21a984714d718e2d0eaab9b51bf9
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Lumis
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Master Hinato! Are you sure you don't have any more questions for our
          candidate?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 5cd68ff4052e42458de8fa25c83cd414
