        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Ah, you're adorable, little Lumis! What's the point of asking questions
          if we can just feel it? If we vibe, we vibe. You know what I'm saying?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 8fdef6028f6d412dab71e216e71f8d4b
